It's not a dream, sifu.

790
01:24:22,660 --> 01:24:26,060
when your father first brought
you here, he told me everything.

791
01:24:26,180 --> 01:24:28,340
he wanted you to learn
wing chun...

792
01:24:28,460 --> 01:24:31,020
to protect yourself
against man...

793
01:24:31,060 --> 01:24:33,540
- and other forces.
- I thought that was all superstition.

794
01:24:33,620 --> 01:24:38,820
superstition is a name the ignorant
give to their ignorance.

795
01:24:38,900 --> 01:24:41,860
you were special then,
and you're special now.

796
01:24:41,940 --> 01:24:44,580
that's why the demon
wants you.

797
01:24:46,860 --> 01:24:50,460
we have spent a lot of time together,
preparing you for this.

798
01:24:54,980 --> 01:24:57,140
good. good.

799
01:24:57,260 --> 01:24:59,540
very good.

800
01:25:01,940 --> 01:25:05,060
