801
01:25:05,140 --> 01:25:06,980
you have no choice.

802
01:25:07,060 --> 01:25:11,620
-you're fighting for more than yourself.
-what are you saying, sifu?

803
01:25:11,700 --> 01:25:15,660
as I told you, this demon
is your inner fear.

804
01:25:15,740 --> 01:25:18,980
It doesn't matter
how many men you defeat.

805
01:25:19,060 --> 01:25:21,420
If you don't conquer
your own fears...

806
01:25:21,500 --> 01:25:24,060
