on to your children...

807
01:25:24,140 --> 01:25:27,260
as your father passed his
on to you.

808
01:25:29,620 --> 01:25:31,460
no.

809
01:25:31,540 --> 01:25:33,380
you will fight him.

810
01:25:38,340 --> 01:25:41,100
when you are
at your absolute peak...

811
01:25:41,180 --> 01:25:43,340
he will come to you.

812
01:25:43,420 --> 01:25:46,700
when the monsoon blow,
be prepared.

813
01:26:53,700 --> 01:26:56,900
mr. lee! mr. lee!

814
01:26:57,020 --> 01:26:59,620
I've been chasing you
all over hong kong.

815
01:26:59,740 --> 01:27:01,740
you should buy a car.

816
01:27:01,860 --> 01:27:05,500
- just a joke.
- I'm philip tan.

817
01:27:05,620 --> 01:27:08,220
I'm a producer. I want to
make a picture with you.

818
01:27:08,300 --> 01:27:11,260
- talk is cheap. pictures are expensive.
- I'm on the level.

819
01:27:11,340 --> 01:27:13,380
you're kato,
and over here...

820
01:27:13,500 --> 01:27:16,420
kato has a small
but loyal following.

821
01:27:16,540 --> 01:27:18,380
something we can build on.

822
01:27:18,500 --> 01:27:21,700
they don't call your show the green
hornet. It's called the kato show.

823
01:27:21,820 --> 01:27:24,740
did you know that?
well, it's true.

824
01:27:24,820 --> 01:27:28,060
when I hear kato is in town,
I consider it a good omen.

825
01:27:28,140 --> 01:27:31,220
- I've got to get back to my family.
- leave tomorrow. give us time.

826
01:27:31,340 --> 01:27:34,580
-I've been away for so long.
-I'll buy you a new ticket, first class.

827
01:27:34,700 --> 01:27:37,500
I'll take care of everything.
one more day, please.

828
01:27:37,580 --> 01:27:40,140
you can't lose.

829
01:27:40,180 --> 01:27:42,020
what's the movie?

830
01:28:05,940 --> 01:28:08,300
action! action!

831
01:28:08,420 --> 01:28:10,860
action!

832
01:28:33,700 --> 01:28:35,620
my brother can't talk right.

833
01:28:35,740 --> 01:28:37,540
he can't walk right.

834
01:28:37,660 --> 01:28:39,860
you have dishonored
my family.

835
01:28:39,940 --> 01:28:41,780
- I have sworn to kill you.
- swearing is easy.

836
01:28:45,340 --> 01:28:49,580
I read your book.
I know all your tricks.

837
01:28:49,660 --> 01:28:52,220
