listen, cheng, give up.

844
01:34:05,380 --> 01:34:07,620
cheng!

845
01:34:07,740 --> 01:34:09,540
ohh!

846
01:34:12,940 --> 01:34:14,740
It's okay, mei.

847
01:34:36,100 --> 01:34:38,740
let's get out of here
before they lynch us.

848
01:35:15,100 --> 01:35:17,940
yeah! hey!

849
01:35:18,060 --> 01:35:21,220
bruce!

850
01:35:56,260 --> 01:35:58,860
bruce!

851
01:35:58,940 --> 01:36:01,020
linda!

852
01:36:01,140 --> 01:36:02,940
bruce!

853
01:36:04,980 --> 01:36:07,540
bruce!

