and one from column "b!"
- mommy!

918
01:41:51,220 --> 01:41:53,020
me happy to build
the railroads...

919
01:41:53,140 --> 01:41:55,580
to dig the mines for you,
mister white man!

920
01:41:57,620 --> 01:42:00,820
