how much longer I can keep this up.

934
01:43:28,540 --> 01:43:31,500
you want it so bad,
don't you?

935
01:43:31,620 --> 01:43:33,820
you want their love so bad.

936
01:43:33,900 --> 01:43:35,740
our love's
not good enough for you.

937
01:43:35,820 --> 01:43:39,500
when I was a kid,
I had all these crazy ideas.

938
01:43:41,220 --> 01:43:45,580
