01:49:24,180 --> 01:49:26,740
but it's over now.

972
01:49:26,820 --> 01:49:31,180
okay, dad, I'll be
the engineer, you be the switcher.

973
01:49:31,300 --> 01:49:33,540
hey, that sounds great.

974
01:49:38,820 --> 01:49:41,380
last shot.

975
01:49:41,460 --> 01:49:44,020
make it great.

976
01:50:01,700 --> 01:50:04,460
- linda, I forgot something.
- what?

977
01:50:05,820 --> 01:50:08,620
I forgot to tell you
I love you.

978
01:50:11,300 --> 01:50:14,340
you know, I don't think you've
ever said that to me before.

979
01:50:14,420 --> 01:50:17,220
yeah, but I meant it
every day.

980
01:50:51,060 --> 01:50:53,820
three weeks before
the opening of enter the dragon...

981
01:50:53,940 --> 01:50:56,140
the film that brought him
international fame...

982
01:50:56,220 --> 01:50:59,180
bruce fell into
a mysterious coma and died.

983
01:50:59,260 --> 01:51:01,140
he was 32.

984
01:51:01,260 --> 01:51:04,980
over 25,000 people attended
his funeral in hong kong...

985
01:51:05,100 --> 01:51:09,140
but I buried him back home
in america to be close to us.

986
01:51:09,220 --> 01:51:13,020
all these years later, people still
wonder about the way he died.

987
01:51:13,140 --> 01:51:15,900
I prefer to remember
the way he lived.

